    <c4d-content-item-heading>
        


  
  
    
    Open your AI future

  





    


    </c4d-content-item-heading>
    <c4d-content-item-copy>
        <c4d-content-item-paragraph>
            <div class="cms-richtext  " id="rich-text-50f4837978" data-dynamic-inner-content="description">
    <p>Get the flexibility you need to make the right AI choices for your business. Choose an open source <a href="https://www.ibm.com/products/watsonx-ai/foundation-models">foundation model</a>, bring your own, or use existing models. And run it across any cloud.</p>

    
    
    
    

</div>
        </c4d-content-item-paragraph>
    </c4d-content-item-copy>
    
    
    
    
    



    
